      ],
      "block_id": "block-0000",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 0,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "对于一个拥有n个样本和m个特征的训练数据集，我们使用线性回归模型进行拟合。样本的特征矩阵为X（一个n×（m＋1)矩阵，已包含偏置项），对应的真实值标签为向量y（一个n×1向量）。模型的参数为向量w（一个(m+1)×1向量）。",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        6,
        266,
        382,
        315
      ],
      "block_id": "block-0001",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 1,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "请根据课件内容，写出以下核心公式：",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        21,
        353,
        330,
        399
      ],
      "block_id": "block-0002",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 2,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "1．代价函数 (Cost Function)",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        58,
        418,
        967,
        471
      ],
      "block_id": "block-0003",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 3,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "请写出线性回归模型中基于均方误差(Mean Squared Error)的代价函数L(w）的矩阵形式。",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        21,
        505,
        336,
        555
      ],
      "block_id": "block-0004",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 4,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "2．数值解 (Normal Equation)",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        52,
        574,
        982,
        692
      ],
      "block_id": "block-0005",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 5,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "当代价函数L(w)是凸函数时，其最优解 $\\pmb { w } ^ { * }$ 可以通过令其梯度为零找到。请写出该最优解的矩阵形式表达式（也称为正规方程解）。",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        21,
        730,
        367,
        775
      ],
      "block_id": "block-0006",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 6,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "3．梯度下降(Gradient Descent)",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        56,
        794,
        606,
        844
      ],
      "block_id": "block-0007",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 7,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "梯度下降是一种通过迭代来最小化代价函数的优化算法。",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        58,
        851,
        765,
        920
      ],
      "block_id": "block-0008",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 8,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "a.请写出代价函数 $\\ b { L } ( \\ b { w } )$ 关于参数w的梯度 $\\frac { \\partial L ( \\boldsymbol { w } ) } { \\partial \\boldsymbol { w } }$ 的矩阵形式表达式。",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        58,
        931,
        776,
        980
      ],
      "block_id": "block-0009",
      "image_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "raw_index": 9,
        "raw_type": "text"
      },
      "page_no": 1,
      "text": "b.基于此梯度，请写出使用梯度下降法更新模型参数w的完整迭代公式。",
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
